ir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dgr1665702635146.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dgr1665702635146.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dgr1665702635146.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dgr1665702635146\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n trigger expand \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__trigger_expand_394543\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Interactive trigger that handles processing to expand a tree item so that subordinate items are shown in the tree view of a Tree widget.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__topic_d117092e1_d117093e1_d117094e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104dgr1665702635146_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__codeblock_c34_drg_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger expand\nparams\n   string control: in ; TREE | LIST | KEYBOARD\n   string item : in\nendparams\n\n; &lt;Your code here&gt;\n\nend ; trigger expand</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__section_w75ab1b7b5_w76ab1b7_w77ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__table_d14468e1_d14469e1_d14470e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Applies to:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Form widgets: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activation:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activated when the user clicks the expand icon of a collapsed tree item, or performs a keyboard action so that the subordinate tree items are shown in the tree view.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default behavior:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Behavior upon completion:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__topic_d83272e1_d83273e1_d83274e1_d83275e1_d83276e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1047090e128\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__li_d44561e1_d44562e1_d44563e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__p_d117098e1_d117099e1_d117100e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">control</span>—input control used by the user; one of:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__li_d44564e1_d44565e1_d44566e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TREE</code>—user clicked in the tree view\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__li_d44567e1_d44568e1_d44569e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LIST</code>—user clicked in the list view\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__li_d44570e1_d44571e1_d44572e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">KEYBOARD</code>—user performed a keyboard action\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__li_d44573e1_d44574e1_d44575e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dgr1665702635146__p_d117101e1_d117102e1_d117103e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">item</span>—value of the selected tree item</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526804\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526804\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "trigger expand Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 trigger expand Interactive trigger that handles processing to expand a tree item so that subordinate items are shown in the tree view of a Tree widget. Explain this code trigger expand params string control: in ; TREE | LIST | KEYBOARD string item : in endparams ; <Your code here> end ; trigger expand Copy Applies to: Form widgets: utree (Tree) Activation: Activated when the user clicks the expand icon of a collapsed tree item, or performs a keyboard action so that the subordinate tree items are shown in the tree view. Default behavior: None Behavior upon completion: None Parameters control —input control used by the user; one of: TREE —user clicked in the tree view LIST —user clicked in the list view KEYBOARD —user performed a keyboard action item —value of the selected tree item Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}